lead_paragraph: Robert Lewandowski scored a brilliant free kick to give Bayern Munich a 1-0 win over Atletico Madrid in their last Champions League Group D outing on Tuesday, ending the 100 percent record of their opponents.

headline.print_headline: Lewandowski's Bayern Goal Ends Perfect Atletico Record
headline.main: Lewandowski's Bayern Goal Ends Perfect Atletico Record
